seoul -lrb- cnn -rrb- north korean leader kim jong un is continuing to rule with an iron fist , having ordered the execution of about 15 senior officials so far this year , according to an assessment by south korean intelligence agents , a lawmaker who attended a closed briefing said .
shin kyung-min , a lawmaker with the new politics alliance for democracy , told a handful of reporters that he had been given the information by the south korean national intelligence service .
cnn can not independently confirm the executions .
the nature of the intelligence supporting the national intelligence service allegations was also not immediately clear .